8C;\">PHP <t t-out=\"object.salary_proposed or '80'\"/></b> per hour.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  Please confirm your availability at your earliest convenience, and feel free to reach out if you have any questions.\n                </p>\n\n                \n                <hr width=\"97%\" style=\"border-style:none;border-top-width:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #101820; border: none; background-color: #ec008c; height: 1px; margin: 16px 0px; opacity: 0.7;\"/>\n\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin: 0; padding: 0; font-size: 13px;\">\n                  Looking forward to working with you!\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  Kind regards,<br/>\n                  <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\"><t t-out=\"user.name or 'TJ'\"/></b><br/>\n                  <t t-out=\"user.email or 'sender@example.com'\"/>\n                </p>\n\n                <!-- Second Divider -->\n                <hr width=\"97%\" style=\"border-style:none;border-top-width:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #101820; border: none; background-color: #ec008c; height: 1px; margin: 16px 0px; opacity: 0.7;\"/>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n",
